title: Xerath Supp S8 - Dealing more Dmg than anyone else

embed.description: League of Legends Preseason/ Season 8 ( Korean) Xerath off meta Support carrying the Botlane as Mage Supp. 3 Matches of me playing Xerath Support and dealing insane Damage! Enjoy the Botlane Fiesta.

body:
Moinsen
